<view class="page kingdom-page">
  <view class="page-head kingdom-head">
    <text class="eyebrow">吗喽王国地图</text>
    <text class="hero-title">{{appMeta.appName}}</text>
    <text class="subtext">{{appMeta.slogan}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="amulet-card status-card {{croissant.statusClass}} kingdom-status">
    <view class="corner-flower"></view>
    <text class="tiny-seal">Croissant 护身符</text>
    <text class="status-name">{{croissant.status}}</text>
    <text class="status-wear">磨损值：{{croissant.wear}}</text>
    <text class="body-text">{{croissant.explanation}}</text>
    <text class="protect-note">{{croissant.advice}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="note-card welcome-card">
    <text>欢迎回到吗喽王国。</text>
    <text>今天也不用立刻做决定。</text>
    <text>先看看 Croissant 现在需要什么。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="map-shell">
    <text class="ribbon-title">王国地点</text>
    <view class="map-grid">
      <view wx:for="{{navItems}}" wx:key="path" class="map-card {{item.color}} {{item.size}}" data-path="{{item.path}}" bindtap="goTo">
        <text class="tiny-seal">{{item.alias}}</text>
        <text class="map-title">{{item.label}}</text>
        <text class="map-subtitle">{{item.subtitle}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <text class="version-note">当前版本：{{appMeta.version}} {{appMeta.stage}}</text>
</view>
